data.description: Point Place Cutie situated on rare 150 X 150' lot! Two concrete driveways with SuperSized Green Space between the house and the garage! HUGE 26 X 32 detached garage, 858SF, parking for 4 cars with ample room. Garage offers walkup attic storage too! Ideal for the home mechanic or storing those Lake Toys! Property also boasts 420SF Workshop behind the home with HVAC system for all seasons. One and a half baths! Finished basement with kitchenette! Upper craft room or fantastic walk-in storage! Don't forget the enclosed sunroom, ideal for the home gardener! Plumbed for a shower in the basement.
